# Downloadable documents (PDFs)
#
# Drop the department's PDFs here using the exact filenames the pages expect,
# and the download buttons switch from the live-portal fallback to the local
# bundled file automatically (see src/data/assets.js -> doc()).
#
# Expected filenames:
#   Academics
#     routine.pdf            — Class routine
#     syllabus2nd.pdf        — Syllabus, 2nd year
#     syllabus3rd.pdf        — Syllabus, 3rd year
#     syllabus4th.pdf        — Syllabus, 4th year
#     syllabusRobotics.pdf   — Minor Degree in Robotics syllabus
#     academicCalender.pdf   — Academic calendar
#     holidayList.pdf        — Holiday list
#   Events
#     magazine.pdf           — Department magazine (EEE-xtravaganza)
#     newsletter.pdf         — Department newsletter
#     fdp1.pdf … fdp5.pdf    — FDP reports (one per programme, newest first)
#   Student Corner — Assignments (digit = year, letter = subject index)
#     theory2a.pdf, theory2b.pdf, theory2c.pdf        — 2nd year theory
#     practical2a.pdf, practical2b.pdf, practical2c.pdf — 2nd year practical
#     theory3a.pdf, theory3b.pdf, theory3c.pdf        — 3rd year theory
#     practical3a.pdf, practical3b.pdf, practical3c.pdf — 3rd year practical
